{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/DescriptionImage1-EN.png?t=1737553631\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead a revolution as a powerful mage against tyrants in a fantasy medieval world. Customize your spells as you desire and make decisions that will benefit your cause in battle. Improve your spells, start the rebellion, and bring down the order!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/DescriptionImage2-EN.png?t=1737553631\" /><strong>Different magic trees</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your spells according to your preferred playstyle. Improve your spells to gain an advantage over your enemies. The magical powers of the fantasy world are under your control. The choice is yours! Which magic tree will you choose and wihch powers will you discover?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/SkillTree2.gif?t=1737553631\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Freedom of choice</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give answers that reflect your personality and manage dialogues as you wish. Take control of your adventure, shape your story with your decisions. Control your character's thoughts and actions and make choices with unique consequences. Command the rebellion as you desire and achieve the glorious victory you dream of!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/Dialogue-2.gif?t=1737553631\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Leader of the revolution</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's up to you to save your people from being slaves of cruel exploitation. Show the wizard guild the way to free your people from the ruthless slavery of tyrants. Take the lead in the fight against tyrants and their henchmen to build a peaceful city for your people. The chains of your people are waiting for you to be broken.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737553631","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/page.bg.jpg?t=1737553631","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/543b361c00caf386119f283a89dd71683844e855/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737553631","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/543b361c00caf386119f283a89dd71683844e855/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737553631","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/DescriptionImage1-EN.png?t=1737553631\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead a revolution as a powerful mage against tyrants in a fantasy medieval world. Customize your spells as you desire and make decisions that will benefit your cause in battle. Improve your spells, start the rebellion, and bring down the order!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/DescriptionImage2-EN.png?t=1737553631\" /><strong>Different magic trees</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your spells according to your preferred playstyle. Improve your spells to gain an advantage over your enemies. The magical powers of the fantasy world are under your control. The choice is yours! Which magic tree will you choose and wihch powers will you discover?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/SkillTree2.gif?t=1737553631\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Freedom of choice</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Give answers that reflect your personality and manage dialogues as you wish. Take control of your adventure, shape your story with your decisions. Control your character's thoughts and actions and make choices with unique consequences. Command the rebellion as you desire and achieve the glorious victory you dream of!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/extras/Dialogue-2.gif?t=1737553631\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Leader of the revolution</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's up to you to save your people from being slaves of cruel exploitation. Show the wizard guild the way to free your people from the ruthless slavery of tyrants. Take the lead in the fight against tyrants and their henchmen to build a peaceful city for your people. The chains of your people are waiting for you to be broken.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","developers":["Moonflake"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390910/header.jpg?t=1737553631","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> x64 architecture<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 500 MB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</st